<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="General View On This — Connect with your neighborhood. Order from local businesses, write reviews, and earn credits through surveys.">
  <title>General View On This — Connect with Your Neighborhood</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/components.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/layout.css">
  <style>
    /* ============================================================
       GVOT Landing Page — Premium Community Platform Design
       ============================================================ */

    /* --- Base Resets for Landing --- */
    .landing-page {
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* --- Navigation --- */
    .landing-nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(232, 227, 218, 0.5);
      transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }
    .landing-nav.scrolled {
      box-shadow: 0 1px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }
    .landing-nav-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
      height: 72px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .landing-nav-brand {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      position: relative;
      cursor: default;
    }
    .landing-nav-brand .brand-tooltip {
      position: absolute;
      top: calc(100% + 8px);
      left: 0;
      background: var(--color-text-primary);
      color: #fff;
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      transition: opacity 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    .landing-nav-brand .brand-tooltip::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -4px;
      left: 16px;
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      background: var(--color-text-primary);
      transform: rotate(45deg);
    }
    .landing-nav-brand:hover .brand-tooltip {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    .landing-nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .landing-nav-link {
      font-size: 0.925rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }
    .landing-nav-link:hover {
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
    }
    .landing-nav-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 24px;
      background: var(--color-accent);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 100px;
      transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
    }
    .landing-nav-cta:hover {
      background: var(--color-accent-hover);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    .landing-nav-mobile {
      display: none;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 4px;
    }
    .landing-nav-mobile span {
      display: block;
      width: 22px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--color-text-primary);
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease;
    }

    /* --- Hero Section --- */
    .landing-hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 120px 2rem 80px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #FAFAF7;
    }

    /* Animated gradient mesh background */
    .hero-mesh {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 20% 40%, rgba(232, 98, 42, 0.08) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 80% 30%, rgba(43, 94, 167, 0.06) 0%, transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 50% 80%, rgba(45, 122, 79, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 70% 70%, rgba(212, 160, 23, 0.04) 0%, transparent 45%);
      animation: meshShift 18s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes meshShift {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1) translate(0, 0); }
      33% { transform: scale(1.05) translate(-1%, 1%); }
      66% { transform: scale(1.02) translate(1%, -0.5%); }
    }

    /* Floating decorative shapes */
    .hero-shape {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      z-index: 0;
      opacity: 0.5;
    }
    .hero-shape-1 {
      width: 400px;
      height: 400px;
      top: -100px;
      right: -80px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232, 98, 42, 0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
      animation: floatShape1 22s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .hero-shape-2 {
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      bottom: -50px;
      left: -60px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(43, 94, 167, 0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
      animation: floatShape2 26s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .hero-shape-3 {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      top: 30%;
      left: 10%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(45, 122, 79, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
      animation: floatShape3 20s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .hero-shape-4 {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      bottom: 25%;
      right: 12%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(212, 160, 23, 0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
      animation: floatShape1 24s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
    }
    @keyframes floatShape1 {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); }
      50% { transform: translate(-20px, 15px) rotate(5deg); }
    }
    @keyframes floatShape2 {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); }
      50% { transform: translate(15px, -20px) rotate(-3deg); }
    }
    @keyframes floatShape3 {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
      50% { transform: translate(10px, 10px); }
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 780px;
    }
    .hero-tagline {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 20px;
      background: rgba(232, 98, 42, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(232, 98, 42, 0.15);
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--color-accent);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
    }
    .hero-tagline svg {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 7vw, 4.5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
      line-height: 1.08;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -1.5px;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.1s forwards;
      opacity: 0;
    }
    .hero-title .hero-highlight {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent) 0%, #d45520 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.3rem);
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      max-width: 580px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.2s forwards;
      opacity: 0;
    }
    .hero-ctas {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.3s forwards;
      opacity: 0;
    }
    .hero-btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 16px 36px;
      background: var(--color-accent);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 100px;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(232, 98, 42, 0.3);
    }
    .hero-btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--color-accent-hover);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(232, 98, 42, 0.4);
    }
    .hero-btn-primary svg {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    .hero-btn-primary:hover svg {
      transform: translateX(3px);
    }
    .hero-btn-secondary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 16px 36px;
      background: var(--color-surface);
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 100px;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border);
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    .hero-btn-secondary:hover {
      border-color: var(--color-text-muted);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }
    .hero-social-proof {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 12px;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.4s forwards;
      opacity: 0;
    }
    .hero-avatars {
      display: flex;
    }
    .hero-avatar {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 2.5px solid #fff;
      margin-left: -10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .hero-avatar:first-child {
      margin-left: 0;
    }
    .hero-avatar-1 { background: var(--color-accent); }
    .hero-avatar-2 { background: var(--color-blue); }
    .hero-avatar-3 { background: var(--color-green); }
    .hero-avatar-4 { background: #8B5CF6; }
    .hero-social-proof-text {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    }
    .hero-social-proof-text strong {
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    /* --- Stats Section --- */
    .landing-stats {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .landing-stats::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(232, 98, 42, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 50%, rgba(43, 94, 167, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .stats-container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .stat-card {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      border-radius: 20px;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }
    .stat-card:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    }
    .stat-icon {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .stat-icon-businesses {
      background: rgba(232, 98, 42, 0.15);
    }
    .stat-icon-businesses svg { color: #E8622A; }
    .stat-icon-surveys {
      background: rgba(45, 122, 79, 0.15);
    }
    .stat-icon-surveys svg { color: #2D7A4F; }
    .stat-icon-orders {
      background: rgba(43, 94, 167, 0.15);
    }
    .stat-icon-orders svg { color: #2B5EA7; }
    .stat-number {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .stat-number .counter {
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .stat-suffix {
      color: rgba(232, 98, 42, 0.9);
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    /* --- How It Works Section --- */
    .landing-how {
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    .section-container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .section-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }
    .section-label {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      color: var(--color-accent);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .section-desc {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .steps-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 3rem;
      position: relative;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    /* Dotted connecting line */
    .steps-grid::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 75px;
      left: calc(16.66% + 30px);
      right: calc(16.66% + 30px);
      height: 2px;
      background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(
        to right,
        var(--color-border) 0px,
        var(--color-border) 8px,
        transparent 8px,
        transparent 16px
      );
    }
    .step-card {
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    .step-deco-number {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
      line-height: 1;
      position: absolute;
      top: -15px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      z-index: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .step-icon-wrap {
      width: 88px;
      height: 88px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .step-card:hover .step-icon-wrap {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
    .step-icon-1 {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FDF0EB 0%, #fce4d8 100%);
      color: var(--color-accent);
    }
    .step-icon-2 {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EBF0FA 0%, #d8e4f8 100%);
      color: var(--color-blue);
    }
    .step-icon-3 {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EBF5F0 0%, #d4eddf 100%);
      color: var(--color-green);
    }
    .step-label {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .step-card h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .step-card p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* --- Features Section --- */
    .landing-features {
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      background: var(--color-surface-2);
    }
    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .feature-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
      border: 1px solid rgba(232, 227, 218, 0.5);
    }
    .feature-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 4px;
    }
    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }
    .feature-card-orders::before {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #E8622A, #f4845f);
    }
    .feature-card-reviews::before {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2B5EA7, #5b8fd9);
    }
    .feature-card-surveys::before {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2D7A4F, #4dab6f);
    }
    .feature-icon-circle {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .feature-icon-orange {
      background: var(--color-accent-light);
    }
    .feature-icon-blue {
      background: var(--color-blue-light);
    }
    .feature-icon-green {
      background: var(--color-green-light);
    }
    .feature-card h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .feature-card p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .feature-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--color-accent);
      transition: gap 0.2s ease;
    }
    .feature-link:hover {
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .feature-link svg {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
    }

    /* --- Social Proof / Trust Section --- */
    .landing-trust {
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    .trust-content {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .testimonials-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }
    .testimonial-card {
      background: var(--color-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 2rem;
      position: relative;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }
    .testimonial-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }
    .testimonial-quote-icon {
      color: var(--color-accent);
      opacity: 0.2;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .testimonial-text {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .testimonial-author {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .testimonial-avatar {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .testimonial-avatar-1 { background: var(--color-accent); }
    .testimonial-avatar-2 { background: var(--color-blue); }
    .testimonial-avatar-3 { background: var(--color-green); }
    .testimonial-name {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.925rem;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
    }
    .testimonial-role {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
    }

    .trust-banner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 1.75rem 2.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EBF5F0 0%, #e0f0e8 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45, 122, 79, 0.15);
      border-radius: 16px;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .trust-shield {
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .trust-banner-text h4 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
    .trust-banner-text p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* --- CTA Section --- */
    .landing-cta {
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E8622A 0%, #d45520 40%, #c4472a 100%);
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .landing-cta::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06) 0%, transparent 50%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .cta-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .landing-cta h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .landing-cta p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 18px 44px;
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--color-accent);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      border-radius: 100px;
      transition: all 0.25s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }
    .cta-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    .cta-btn svg {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    .cta-btn:hover svg {
      transform: translateX(3px);
    }

    /* --- Footer --- */
    .landing-footer {
      padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem;
      background: #1a1a2e;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    }
    .footer-container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .footer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1.2fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .footer-brand-name {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .footer-brand-desc {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 280px;
    }
    .footer-socials {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .footer-social-link {
      width: 38px;
      height: 38px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      transition: background 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
    }
    .footer-social-link:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      color: #fff;
    }
    .footer-col-title {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }
    .footer-link {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }
    .footer-link:hover {
      color: #fff;
    }
    .footer-contact-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    }
    .footer-contact-item svg {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 2px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    }
    .footer-bottom {
      padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .footer-copyright {
      font-size: 0.825rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    }
    .footer-bottom-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .footer-bottom-link {
      font-size: 0.825rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }
    .footer-bottom-link:hover {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    }

    /* --- Scroll Animation --- */
    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    .reveal.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* ============================================================
       Responsive Design
       ============================================================ */

    /* Tablet landscape / small desktop */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
      .testimonials-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
      .testimonials-grid .testimonial-card:last-child {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .footer-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 2.5rem;
      }
    }

    /* Tablet portrait */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .landing-nav-links {
        display: none;
      }
      .landing-nav-mobile {
        display: flex;
      }
      .landing-nav-links.open {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        position: absolute;
        top: 72px;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: stretch;
      }
      .landing-nav-links.open .landing-nav-cta {
        text-align: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .landing-hero {
        min-height: auto;
        padding: 120px 1.5rem 60px;
      }
      .hero-title {
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      }

      .stats-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 1.25rem;
      }

      .steps-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2.5rem;
        max-width: 400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .steps-grid::before {
        display: none;
      }
      .step-deco-number {
        font-size: 4rem;
      }

      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .testimonials-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .testimonials-grid .testimonial-card:last-child {
        max-width: none;
      }

      .trust-banner {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      }

      .hero-ctas {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .hero-btn-primary,
      .hero-btn-secondary {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 320px;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .footer-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
      }
      .footer-bottom {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer-bottom-links {
        justify-content: center;
      }
    }

    /* Mobile */
    @media (max-width: 375px) {
      .landing-nav-inner {
        padding: 0 1rem;
      }
      .landing-hero {
        padding: 100px 1rem 48px;
      }
      .landing-stats,
      .landing-how,
      .landing-features,
      .landing-trust,
      .landing-cta {
        padding-left: 1rem;
        padding-right: 1rem;
      }
      .stat-card {
        padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
      }
      .feature-card {
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      }
      .testimonial-card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }
      .footer-container {
        padding: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="landing-page">

  <!-- ============================================================
       Navigation
       ============================================================ -->
  <nav class="landing-nav" id="landingNav">
    <div class="landing-nav-inner">
      <div class="landing-nav-brand">
        GVOT
        <span class="brand-tooltip">General View On This</span>
      </div>
      <button class="landing-nav-mobile" aria-label="Toggle navigation" id="navToggle">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </button>
      <div class="landing-nav-links" id="navLinks">
        <a href="/reviews" class="landing-nav-link">Browse Businesses</a>
        <a href="/auth/login" class="landing-nav-link">Log In</a>
        <a href="/auth/register" class="landing-nav-cta">Join Free</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ============================================================
       Hero Section
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="landing-hero">
    <div class="hero-mesh"></div>
    <div class="hero-shape hero-shape-1"></div>
    <div class="hero-shape hero-shape-2"></div>
    <div class="hero-shape hero-shape-3"></div>
    <div class="hero-shape hero-shape-4"></div>

    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-tagline">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg>
        Your neighborhood, connected
      </div>

      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Discover & support your <span class="hero-highlight">local community</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Earn credits by sharing your opinions. Spend them at local businesses.
        Write honest reviews. Build real community trust.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="/auth/register" class="hero-btn-primary">
          Get Started Free
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/reviews" class="hero-btn-secondary">Browse Businesses</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-social-proof">
        <div class="hero-avatars">
          <div class="hero-avatar hero-avatar-1">S</div>
          <div class="hero-avatar hero-avatar-2">M</div>
          <div class="hero-avatar hero-avatar-3">A</div>
          <div class="hero-avatar hero-avatar-4">R</div>
        </div>
        <span class="hero-social-proof-text">Join <strong><%= (stats.totalBusinesses + stats.totalOrders + 50) %>+</strong> community members</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       Stats Section
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="landing-stats">
    <div class="stats-container">
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card reveal">
          <div class="stat-icon stat-icon-businesses">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20 4H4v2h16V4zm1 10v-2l-1-5H4l-1 5v2h1v6h10v-6h4v6h2v-6h1zm-9 4H6v-4h6v4z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-number">
            <span class="counter" data-target="<%= stats.totalBusinesses %>">0</span><span class="stat-suffix">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-label">Local Businesses</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card reveal">
          <div class="stat-icon stat-icon-surveys">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zM9 17H7v-7h2v7zm4 0h-2V7h2v10zm4 0h-2v-4h2v4z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-number">
            <span class="counter" data-target="<%= stats.totalSurveys %>">0</span><span class="stat-suffix">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-label">Surveys Available</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card reveal">
          <div class="stat-icon stat-icon-orders">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18 6h-2c0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4S8 3.79 8 6H6c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V8c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-6-2c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2h-4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2zm6 16H6V8h2v2c0 .55.45 1 1 1s1-.45 1-1V8h4v2c0 .55.45 1 1 1s1-.45 1-1V8h2v12z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-number">
            <span class="counter" data-target="<%= stats.totalOrders %>">0</span><span class="stat-suffix">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-label">Orders Placed</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       How It Works
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="landing-how">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <div class="section-label">How It Works</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Three Steps to Community Connection</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Start supporting local businesses and earning credits in minutes. No credit card needed.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step-card reveal">
          <div class="step-deco-number">01</div>
          <div class="step-icon-wrap step-icon-1">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="38" height="38" fill="currentColor"><path d="M15 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm-9-2V7H4v3H1v2h3v3h2v-3h3v-2H6zm9 4c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="step-label">Step 01</div>
          <h3>Create Your Account</h3>
          <p>Sign up in seconds as a community member or local business owner. Always free.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card reveal">
          <div class="step-deco-number">02</div>
          <div class="step-icon-wrap step-icon-2">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="38" height="38" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-7 3c1.93 0 3.5 1.57 3.5 3.5S13.93 13 12 13s-3.5-1.57-3.5-3.5S10.07 6 12 6zm7 13H5v-.23c0-.62.28-1.2.76-1.58C7.47 15.82 9.64 15 12 15s4.53.82 6.24 2.19c.48.38.76.97.76 1.58V19z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="step-label">Step 02</div>
          <h3>Share Your Opinions</h3>
          <p>Complete quick community surveys on local topics and earn 1 credit per survey.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card reveal">
          <div class="step-deco-number">03</div>
          <div class="step-icon-wrap step-icon-3">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="38" height="38" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18 6h-2c0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4S8 3.79 8 6H6c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V8c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-6-2c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2h-4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2zm6 16H6V8h2v2c0 .55.45 1 1 1s1-.45 1-1V8h4v2c0 .55.45 1 1 1s1-.45 1-1V8h2v12z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="step-label">Step 03</div>
          <h3>Order from Locals</h3>
          <p>Spend your credits on pickup orders at local businesses. Support your neighborhood.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       Features
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="landing-features">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <div class="section-label">Features</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Everything Your Community Needs</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Built for neighborhoods that want to stay connected and support each other.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card feature-card-orders reveal">
          <div class="feature-icon-circle feature-icon-orange">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="#E8622A"><path d="M18 6h-2c0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4S8 3.79 8 6H6c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V8c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-6-2c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2h-4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2zm6 16H6V8h2v2c0 .55.45 1 1 1s1-.45 1-1V8h4v2c0 .55.45 1 1 1s1-.45 1-1V8h2v12z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Credit-Based Orders</h3>
          <p>No money changes hands. Earn credits through surveys and spend them on pickup orders from local businesses.</p>
          <a href="/auth/register" class="feature-link">
            Start earning
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card feature-card-reviews reveal">
          <div class="feature-icon-circle feature-icon-blue">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="#2B5EA7"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Honest Reviews</h3>
          <p>Reviews can never be deleted. Radical transparency means businesses earn trust through quality, not censorship.</p>
          <a href="/reviews" class="feature-link">
            Browse reviews
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card feature-card-surveys reveal">
          <div class="feature-icon-circle feature-icon-green">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="#2D7A4F"><path d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zM9 17H7v-7h2v7zm4 0h-2V7h2v10zm4 0h-2v-4h2v4z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Community Surveys</h3>
          <p>Share opinions on local topics like restaurants, events, and transportation. Each survey earns you 1 credit.</p>
          <a href="/auth/register" class="feature-link">
            Take a survey
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       Social Proof / Trust
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="landing-trust">
    <div class="trust-content">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <div class="section-label">Community Voices</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Trusted by Neighbors Like You</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Real people. Real opinions. Real community impact.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
          <div class="testimonial-quote-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M6 17h3l2-4V7H5v6h3zm8 0h3l2-4V7h-6v6h3z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">I love that the reviews here feel genuine. No censorship, no filtered feedback. It helped me find the best coffee shop in my area.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar testimonial-avatar-1">SP</div>
            <div>
              <div class="testimonial-name">Sarah P.</div>
              <div class="testimonial-role">Community Member</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
          <div class="testimonial-quote-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M6 17h3l2-4V7H5v6h3zm8 0h3l2-4V7h-6v6h3z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">As a small business owner, GVOT gives me direct access to what my community actually wants. The survey credits system is brilliant.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar testimonial-avatar-2">MK</div>
            <div>
              <div class="testimonial-name">Marcus K.</div>
              <div class="testimonial-role">Local Business Owner</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
          <div class="testimonial-quote-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M6 17h3l2-4V7H5v6h3zm8 0h3l2-4V7h-6v6h3z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">Completing surveys takes just minutes, and the credits add up fast. I've already placed three orders at places I wouldn't have tried otherwise.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar testimonial-avatar-3">AL</div>
            <div>
              <div class="testimonial-name">Amira L.</div>
              <div class="testimonial-role">Active Contributor</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-banner reveal">
        <div class="trust-shield">
          <svg width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#2D7A4F"><path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm-2 16l-4-4 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l6.59-6.59L18 9l-8 8z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-banner-text">
          <h4>Radical Transparency Guarantee</h4>
          <p>Reviews on GVOT can never be deleted. Businesses and customers build real trust through honest, permanent feedback.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       CTA Section
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="landing-cta">
    <div class="cta-content reveal">
      <h2>Ready to Support Your Community?</h2>
      <p>Join your neighbors on GVOT. It's free, it's local, and it makes a real difference.</p>
      <a href="/auth/register" class="cta-btn">
        Create Your Free Account
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       Footer
       ============================================================ -->
  <footer class="landing-footer">
    <div class="footer-container">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <!-- Brand Column -->
        <div>
          <div class="footer-brand-name">General View On This</div>
